verbose_text: UBE2L3 / rs140490 genotype was correlated with control over basal NF-kappaB activation in healthy human individuals for both B cells (p = 0.0026, r 2 = 0.21) and monocytes (p = 0.022, r 2 = 0.13) (XREF_FIG C), tending to a linear effect according to genotype, consistent with the effect of rs140490 on UBE2L3 expression for these cell types.
